Business:
[Increase the corporate income tax rate for companies that have a pay ratio between the chief executive officer and the median worker above 50 to 1, raising the rate](https://berniesanders.com/issues/corporate-accountability-and-democracy/)
• 0.5 percentage points if the ratio is between 50 and 100 to 1;
• 1 percentage point if the ratio is between 100 and 200 to 1;
• 2 percentage points if the ratio is between 200 and 300 to 1;
• 3 percentage points if the ratio is between 300 and 400 to 1;
• 4 percentage points if the ratio is between 400 and 500 to 1; and
• 5 percentage points if the ratio is more than 500 to 1

